# brave-search
# MCP server for Brave Search API

@toollean v0.1
@tool brave_web_search
@desc Search the web using Brave Search API
@in query:str Search query
@in count:int?=10 Number of results (1-20)
@in offset:int? Pagination offset
@in country:str? Country code (e.g. US, GB, DE)
@in search_lang:str? Search language (e.g. en, de, fr)
@in freshness:str?(pd/pw/pm/py) Time filter: past day/week/month/year
@in safesearch:str?(off/moderate/strict) Safe search level

@toollean v0.1
@tool brave_local_search
@desc Search for local businesses and places
@in query:str Local search query (e.g. 'pizza near me')
@in count:int?=5 Number of results
